, \'bai b\'e3tu cu el \'een podea.}{\f27\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\f446\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Rog pe Venera}{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'feia voastr\'e3 s\'e3 m\'e3 ierte. Ma\'bain\'e3ria f\'e3cut\'e3 de mine e un model prea}{\f27\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 
