\par }{\f446\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Venera}{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'feia voastr\'e3, aurul provine dintr-o surs\'e3 otr\'e3vit\'e3.
