\'e3 spiritelor vii ale sfin\'feilor no\'batri str\'e3mo\'bai.}{\f27\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\f446\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai totu\'bai acesta este aur, spuse Marele St\'e3p\'een, nehot\'e3rit, \'bai nu reprezint\'e3 dec\'eet un schimb pentru p\'e3g\'ee
nul condamnat pentru tic\'e3lo\'baia lui. Pherl, cred c\'e3 e\'bati prea critic. \'ce\'bai retrase m\'eena pe care o \'eentinsese dup\'e3 aur.}{\f27\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\f446\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af S}{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'eente\'fei \'een\'feelepciunea \'eentruchipat\'e3, Venera\'feia voastr\'e3, zise Ponyets. S\'e3 cuget\'e3m: prin liberarea unui p\'e3g\'een, str\'e3mo
