\par }{\f446\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af }{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'aai care ar fi acest lucru? \'eel \'eembie Pherl cu un z\'eembet \'bairet. S\'eent sigur c\'e3 ceea ce-mi spui nu reprezint\'e3
