\par }{\f446\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'af Da, bine}{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 \'een\'feeles. (Pherl \'ee\'bai \'eempreun\'e3 m\'eeinile \'bai le duse la b\'e3rbie). Nu te judec. St\'eeng\'e3cia a fost deliberat\'e3, s\'ee
nt sigur. A\'ba fi putut s\'e3 atrag aten\'feia Venera\'feiei sale asupra }{\i\f27\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 acestui }{\f443\fs20\cf1\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 lucru dac\'e3 a\'ba fi fost sigur de motiva\'feie. \'cen locul t\'e3u a\'ba
